{"word":"G1918 - ἐπιγαμβρεύω - epigambreúō - ep-ee-gam-bryoo'-o - Marry","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιγαμβρεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epigambreúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-gam-bryoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Marry</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விவாகம் பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"to be related to by marriage, enter into affinity with"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G1062 - γάμος - gámos - gam'-os/1062\">G1062</a>; to <i>form affinity with</i>, that is, (specifically) in a levirate way: - marry.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}